snippet.title: Battleship: The Video Game Wii Trailer
snippet.description:
February 11, 2012 12:05 AM - Battleship: The Video Game will be release in the US on May 15, 2012. Battleship thrusts you headlong into an Earth facing an unknown aquatic alien menace. As Cole Mathis, the U.S. naval fleet's "Boots on the Ground", you must prove yourself worthy as an elite soldier and help defeat the enemy. Find your inner soldier and stop the alien threat before it's too late!

Visit my channel at http://www.youtube.com/user/josegruiz80?feature=mhee for more Wii and Wii U News, Trailers, and More.
Don't forget to subscribe.
